# Xcode per-user state — never commit
**/xcuserdata/
**/*.xcuserstate

# SwiftPM resolved package versions for the Xcode project (Linux SPM
# uses Package.resolved at the repo root; this is the duplicate Xcode
# writes inside the .xcodeproj which we don't track).
**/Package.resolved
**/swiftpm/

# DerivedData / build artifacts (defaults are user-specific anyway)
**/build/
**/DerivedData/

# macOS Finder
.DS_Store
**/.DS_Store
